  "description": "<i>Alfabet ?mierci</i> is an adventure game with graphics presented in the form of photographs. The action takes place in D?by village and in the surrounding countryside. The game begins with an alarming phone call from a friend who dies in a mysterious accident a while later. The train trip to the hometown results with a strong blow to the back of the head. Tomasz Antkowiak wake up on the D?by railway platform where the game begins. The main task requires solving a series of occult mysteries leading to the killer of your your friend. The character may carry up an unlimited number of items that can be used and combined. The game screen is divided into inventory/action panel, commentary field and photograph showing the current location. The player may talk with each encountered character, however a special caution is required because the wrong answers may result in death. Travelling is possible by walking through each location or using the plan of the village.",
